Place the generated file at `certora/harnesses/{{ harness_name }}.sol` on the VFS using the `put_file` tool.
The contract identifier MUST be exactly `{{ harness_name }}`.

**Important**: Prior executions of this workflow may mean the harness already exists on the VFS. So long as
the file exists with an implementation that satisfies the above instructions, you *may* deliver it unchanged.

Once the harness has been generated, call the `result` tool with the relative path to the generated file and
